, they confront a malevolent force in the form of a demonic nun.", cast: ["Demian Bichir","Taissa Farmiga","Jonas Bloquet"]), Movie(title: "The Invisible Man", image: UIImage(named: "The Invisible Man")!, releasedYear: "2020", movieRating: "7.1", boxOffice: "143.2M", moviePlot: "After staging his own suicide, a crazed scientist uses his power to become invisible to stalk and terrorize his ex-girlfriend. When the police refuse to believe her story, she decides to take matters into her own hands and fight back.", cast: ["Elisabeth Moss","Oliver Jackson-Cohen","Harriet Dyer"])])

